Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

; Removes the startup delay from MBAM (speeds up first check in and drive encryption)
[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\MBAM]
“NoStartupDelay”=dword:00000001


;These settings are *NOT* recommended outside of testing.  This will cause the client to constantly check in with the server.
